ons at 14.5 kHz achieve sufficiently\nhigh gain (G = 5) to generate significant volumes of closed flux lasting 1-2\ninjector periods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Mar 2020 19:05:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-16"}
